The paper deals with image processing and computer vision techniques for fingerprint denoising and inpainting using Convolutional Neural Networks. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves deep learning techniques, which makes cs.LG (Machine Learning) another likely category. The use of segmentation and loss functions also suggests cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as a possible category. The paper also involves multimedia processing, which makes cs.MM (Multimedia) a likely category. Finally, since the paper deals with security and privacy-related issues, cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) is also a possible category.
